<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>289</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawiah a um um, buh lakhawm dingte?
 Gitlohna lo a buh phal lakhawm ding?
 Thutak kawite manga sep ding ahi,
 Buh at zaw ma'n kuomah chawl thei puon a.

[V2]
 Khawi ah buh atte, kuo a hung ding?
 Buh at zawh tieng lopina chuh chang dingin;
 Kuo a ei huh ding, lakhawm dingin,
 Gitlohna lo a buh pha um haw chu?

[V3]
 2. Mun tinah chieh unla, a va hawlkhawm un,
 Ham sang mahleh buh chuh mu zel unla;
 Muntin hawl unla, kaht le hengilh kiu,
 Van Ina di'n a bawnin lakhawm un.

[V4]
 3. Buh amin tai, gamtin, muntin a um,
 Tu'n khawvel in buh lakphat ding a ngak;
 Buh at mi atawm, nasep ding atam,
 A lak vak loh uleh, tampi mang ding.

[V5]
 4. Mihiem chate na kawiteu hun pan un,
 Sana buhvui haw chu lakhawm dingin;
 Lo neipa hung masang sieh in semun,
 Tichun, vanah kipahna chang tan lau.</lyrics>
<title>WHERE ARE THE REAPERS?</title>
</song>